# =================================================================
# 🛡️ FSD-car 统一主干仓库 Git 忽略契约
# =================================================================

# --- 1. 系统与通用临时文件 ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp
*.bak

# --- 2. 阶段一 (mujoco-nmpc-car) 忽略项 ---
mujoco-nmpc-car/__pycache__/
mujoco-nmpc-car/*.py[cod]
mujoco-nmpc-car/*$py.class
mujoco-nmpc-car/c_generated_code/
mujoco-nmpc-car/acados_ocp.json
mujoco-nmpc-car/acados/
mujoco-nmpc-car/*.log
mujoco-nmpc-car/MUJOCO_LOG.TXT

# --- 3. 阶段二 (zenoh-rs) 忽略项 ---
# 必须忽略 Rust 编译生成的 target 文件夹（动辄几百MB，严禁提交！）
zenoh-rs/target/

# 如果你希望在 GitHub 上保留 Cargo 依赖锁定文件，请保持下面这行注释状态
# 如果不想提交它，可以取消注释
# zenoh-rs/Cargo.lock